{"tid":672432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］全日空往香港航班疑引擎故障折返","createTime":"2018-05-21T03:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T05:17:25.000Z","uid":37757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c855ebd8d1892c073178ea4de9413dc083bfdf98","tid":672432,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:54:48.000Z","msg":"２１日午前９時５０分ごろ、成田空港を離陸しようと搭乗橋を離れた香港行き全日空８０９便ボーイング７６７型機（乗客乗員１３７人）で、機内に煙が充満するトラブルがあった。同機は直後に搭乗橋に戻り、乳幼児を含む乗客全員と乗員を降ろした。乗客４人が体調不良を訴えたが、救急搬送はされなかった。<br />\n<br />\n国土交通省成田空港事務所や全日空などによると、機体後部にある電力供給などに使われる補助動力装置（ＡＰＵ）の煙が、客室や操縦室に入り込んだとみられる。同事務所などは詳しい原因を調べる。<br />\n　成田空港は一時、Ａ滑走路が閉鎖されたが、他の航空機の運航に影響はなかった。"},{"pid":"5d38cfb895d21848bdb2e0aa4d169df40a7d1d7b","tid":672432,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:56:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機内に煙が充満</span>"},{"pid":"29f56088d9ec442ad12a60957dee66377ed71ed1","tid":672432,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"jal123<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b7f4a91aec23f4fac3b3b162d7f47b36aaa6ba","tid":672432,"uid":33477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29f56088d9ec442ad12a60957dee66377ed71ed1","tid":672432,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"jal123<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:59:42.000Z","msg":"冇起到飛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6781fa6e8855617d15db47ce6552360519120bf6","tid":672432,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29f56088d9ec442ad12a60957dee66377ed71ed1","tid":672432,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"jal123<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T04:00:01.000Z","msg":"納dee驚唔驚<im